飲 仲送多士<br />\n佢質素絕對對得起個價<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M0M33ES.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM0M33ES.jpg&h=77a8ce08&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T18:15:20.000Z","msg":"咪係 唔知班人係咪未出過社會做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日話難食難食 <br />\n<br />\n我真係拍心口講 龍門晚餐5x蚊有野飲絕對對得住個價錢<br />\n<br />\n最多你可以講佢無獲氣  食落似大家樂大快活<br />\n<br />\n你用一個西餐$399set 黎對比,龍門當然可以叫做難食<br />\n<br />\n但呢晚市5x價錢黎講 話難食絕對稱唔上<br />\n<br />\n根本大撚把茶記晚夜 6,7十蚊 都係得兜垃圾碟頭飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de47bf8b33a9fefc1006f27b7adee9fdf2114cda","tid":2096531,"uid":37413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9cff32f4948b72080f190a3ea6a6ee58892400b6","tid":2096531,"uid":51583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T16:09:06.000Z","msg":"係一開始攪得越黎越大D人唔鍾意<br />\n又運輸又美容又水電<br />\nD人覺得佢想食晒黃圈市場<br />\n之後就好多攻擊出現"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T18:20:03.000Z","msg":"個市場咁大邊有可能食得晒吖講真"},{"pid":"4769022ec606aad3621ae19a4698b5427cfc9408","tid":2096531,"uid":59518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c8090b550c013b956fad74fcc343a92a4cbabd7","tid":2096531,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T15:25:51.000Z","msg":"黑社會背景夠唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T18:24:43.000Z","msg":"個個post都入去話人黑社會<br />\n唔講邊個堂口你都話埋邊個社團先有討論價值啦垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}